title: F*** YOUR EXCUSES
itunes:title: F*** YOUR EXCUSES
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
Some people aren't meant to be in your life forever. If someone hits you with doubt and questions your choices, it's time to surround yourself with LIONS AND WOLVES. Enough with the excuses. It's time to stand out from the pack. One of the Best Motivational Speeches Ever and our first release with Cole "The Wolf" DaSilva.


Music by Paul Elhart (http://bit.ly/2SiEaIN).
